{"tid":1233384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係割蓆但有無人答到，而家佔龍和道做乜？","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:35.000Z","uid":218575,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18924ed46fd518eb4a117b3fb5d21b5273bcb915","tid":1233384,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"好簡單一個問題 <br />\n你留守係做乜野<br />\n起road block係做乜？<br />\n<br />\n唔係唔俾你地做 <br />\n但做要做得有意義 <br />\n到而家都未有人答到佔黎做乜<br />\n淨係講人地有人地做法 <br />\n理得人點做  但最起碼你講得出佔龍和道意義掛？<br />\n人數仲要咁少 <br />\n佔龍和道做乜？ <br />\n<br />\n呢個post無篤灰無割蓆。"},{"pid":"f86166fdb2bd5a6055f2c8a84c6bdc4e1aab9a5f","tid":1233384,"uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:40:07.000Z","msg":"想知依家燒垃圾桶有乜作用"},{"pid":"361f9b7f150ea1e186eb8bf362e35d991b1fa7fa","tid":1233384,"uid":112282,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:41:54.000Z","msg":"龍和道未12點已經佔咗啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心覺得起同唔起roadblock無分別 唔覺得係鬼<br />\n不過同意現埸手足大家多啲留意 唔好亂鳩跟人做野"},{"pid":"b94c8a4d2426bb3ecfa76c6af79b762bc9469004","tid":1233384,"uid":218575,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f86166fdb2bd5a6055f2c8a84c6bdc4e1aab9a5f","tid":1233384,"uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:40:07.000Z","msg":"想知依家燒垃圾桶有乜作用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"成班有勇無謀 唔知做乜<br />\n問有咩意義都答唔到"},{"pid":"09562f8388fbdd7b1377cf4835a711f103015bbd","tid":1233384,"uid":218575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"361f9b7f150ea1e186eb8bf362e35d991b1fa7fa","tid":1233384,"uid":112282,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:41:54.000Z","msg":"龍和道未12點已經佔咗啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心覺得起同唔起roadblock無分別 唔覺得係鬼<br />\n不過同意